Oriole Burevitch Laboratory : \n \n Current Usage: \n \n The laboratory building is used for autopsies of stranded mammals, marine-related research, and other usage to support the Department of Biology and Marine Biology.
Kresge Greenhouse   :  \n \n Departments: \n \n Biology & Marine Biology \n \n The Kresge Greenhouse is a classroom-laboratory which allows for a year-round supply of salt marsh environment plants to be cultured for teaching and research.
